Permits Granted

Build

grant <- ec %>% filter(Status %in% c("EC Granted","EC Granted - Processed offline")) %>% distinct()
grant$duplicate <- duplicated(grant$Proposal)
extract_after_colon <- function(input) {
  split_string <- strsplit(input, ":")
  extracted_text <- sapply(split_string, function(x) trimws(x[2]))
  return(extracted_text)
}

# Applying the function to the input vector
grant$submit <- extract_after_colon(grant$Date_1) %>% dmy()
grant$grant <- extract_after_colon(grant$Date_2) %>% dmy()

grant$time <- as.duration(grant$grant - grant$submit)/ddays(1)
summary(grant$time)
##    Min. 1st Qu.  Median    Mean 3rd Qu.    Max.    NA's 
## -5479.0    71.0   103.0   136.2   161.0  1708.0      41
#Exclude if length  less than 0

grant <- grant %>% filter(time >=0) #Some obs have negative grant time

dist <- grant %>% group_by(District,State) %>% summarise(avg = mean(time),sd = sd(time), count = n(),most = names(table(Category))[which.max(table(Category))])
